#  Student Marks Analyzer (Pandas Series Project)

##  Overview
This project is a simple **Student Marks Analysis System** built using Python and Pandas Series. It allows users to input student marks and perform basic statistical analysis.

---

##  Features
- Input student names and marks dynamically
- Find topper of the class
- Calculate average marks
- Identify highest and lowest scores
- Filter students scoring above 75
- Detect failed students (<40)
- Add new students dynamically
- Update existing student marks
- Sort marks in descending order

---

##  Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas (Series)
